## Stack

- **Next.js 16.2.4** with the App Router (`src/app/`)
- **React 19**
- **TypeScript**
- **Tailwind CSS v4** — imported via `@import "tailwindcss"` in `globals.css`, configured through `@tailwindcss/postcss`
